# Plan 3: Core Layout & Navigation

## Goal
Build the public-facing layout and navigation bar, ensuring mobile responsiveness and smooth transitions.

## Tasks
- [ ] Create the main `RootLayout` in `app/layout.tsx` with the chosen font (Inter/Outfit).
- [ ] Create a `Navbar` component with links: Music, Videos, Tour, Blog, Gallery, About.
- [ ] Implement a mobile menu (hamburger) using a Sheet component (shadcn/ui).
- [ ] Create a `Footer` component with social links and newsletter signup placeholder.
- [ ] Add Framer Motion for page transitions (optional, or simple fade-in).
- [ ] Ensure the layout has a placeholder for the persistent music player at the bottom.
